  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the frequency and the clinical course of
      postoperative hyperthyroidism following surgery of tertiary hyperparathyroidism (THP) and to
      determine the diagnostic value of thyroglobulin in this setting.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
